# Animica Contrib â€” .gitignore
# Focus: thumbnails, ad-hoc exports, and stray archives.
# NOTE: We intentionally COMMIT canonical build artifacts (tokens builds, icon sprite,
# email HTML, press zips listed below). Do not add those to ignores.

# --- OS/editor cruft ----------------------------------------------------------
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/*~
**/*.bak
**/*.tmp
**/*.orig
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/

# --- Thumbnails ---------------------------------------------------------------
**/thumbs/
**/thumbnails/
**/*-thumb.*
**/*_thumb.*
**/*-preview.*
**/*_preview.*

# --- Generic export folders (from design tools) -------------------------------
# Keep canonical "build" outputs tracked; this targets ad-hoc export dirs only.
**/export/
**/exports/
**/Export/
**/Exports/
**/renders/
**/render/
**/out/
**/outputs/
**/previews/
**/screenshots/

# --- Archives (ZIPs) ----------------------------------------------------------
# Ignore random zips EXCEPT the official, versioned press bundles.
**/*.zip
!press/logos/animica-logo.zip
!press/kits/press-kit.zip

# --- Caches & envs (if any scripts live here) --------------------------------
**/node_modules/
**/.pnpm-store/
**/.cache/
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/__pycache__/

# --- Do NOT ignore committed build artifacts ---------------------------------
# (Documented for clarity; the negations ensure they remain tracked.)
!tokens/build/**
!icons/sprite/sprite.svg
!email/templates/**
!explorer/themes/**
